						<p>Hi there. Great post and site. In regards to hoisting, there was a little confusion (at least for me) in your explanation about function hoisting. It should be made clear that function declarations get fully hoisted to the top, while function expressions behave like variables. Maybe even add that function declarations get hoisted and turn into an expression at the top. Just my opinion.</p>
						
